pull_request.title: Switch back to subprocess.run
pull_request.body:
This PR switches our helpers.run_subprocess function back to using Python's `subprocess.run`. It also includes a pure python implementation of test_free which serves as an alternative fix for #852. The previous fix for #852 in commit 346305fc added a timeout to our subprocess calls which we've been hitting in CI.

The timeout was a less-than-ideal solution for killing long running jobs since it is based on wall-clock time.

pull_request.body:
Bumps [oqs-sys/liboqs](https://github.com/Open-Quantum-Safe/liboqs) from `fb5484c` to `1ead54f`.
Commits
  • 1ead54f Remove round 2 Dilithium KATs (#898)
  • 1256e3b Mb randloop (#897)
  • bd4d09d Sync upstream with copy_from_upstram / pqcrystals pull (#891)
  • fc35e09 Update copy_from_pqclean / copy_from_upstream (#883)
  • d183ccd remove docker auth for now (#885)
  • a152118 Update list of Rainbow algorithms in README
